data.description:
Looking to live on the golf course look no further with a beautiful view of hole 1 on the West course.  This immaculate, move-in ready home in the stunning gated active adult community of Robson Ranch is a must see.  This open and inviting concept is perfect for gatherings with friends and family.  Spacious primary bedroom suite, custom closet system and a golf cart garage a bonus.This Prestigious 55+ community at Robson Ranch is an active lifestyle community with amenities galore. Clubhouse, Golf, Tennis, Pickleball, Fitness Center, Creative Arts, Dog Parks, Pool, Baseball field and many clubs to join. 2022 evolution golf cart 4 seater included with good offer. 
Back on the market not due to inspection
